flowchart TD
  A[POST /auth/register] --> B[Policy mode check]
  B --> C[auth_users plus auth_credentials]
  C --> D[Optional email verification]
  E[POST /auth/login] --> F[Rate limit check]
  F --> G[Password verify]
  G -->|success| H[Set session and CSRF cookies]
  G -->|failure| I[Generic error and audit]
  H --> J[GET /auth/me]
  J --> K[Protected browser routes]
  K --> L[POST /auth/logout]
